      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "luke",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "Luke 5:27",
      "text": "ܒܬܪ ܗܠܝܢ ܢܦܩ ܝܫܘܥ ܘܚܙܐ ܡܟܤܐ ܕܫܡܗ ܠܘܝ ܕܝܬܒ ܒܝܬ ܡܟܤܐ ܘܐܡܪ ܠܗ ܬܐ ܒܬܪܝ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:luke.5.28",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "luke",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "Luke 5:28",
      "text": "ܘܫܒܩ ܟܠ ܡܕܡ ܘܩܡ ܐܙܠ ܒܬܪܗ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
